        "activityType": "observational-study",
        "name": "CPB Registry Observational Data Collection",
        "description": "Prospective observational registry study in which hemolysis indices were recorded across routine clinical CPB procedures. Flow rates and pump speeds were set by clinical need, not by experimental protocol. No randomisation, blinding, or controlled manipulation of independent variables was performed. Data were collected under IRB approval at three participating centres over 18 months."
      },
